1
00:00:00,270 --> 00:00:01,270
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,340 --> 00:00:03,270
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,340 --> 00:00:05,410
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:06,880
This concerns Park Min Jun.

5
00:00:08,180 --> 00:00:11,280
The hit-and-run driver
who tried to kill your son...

6
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:14,020
was...

7
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:20,660
your wife,

8
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,060
Oh Jung Ran.

9
00:00:26,260 --> 00:00:27,270
What?

10
00:00:33,100 --> 00:00:34,570
You. Say that again.

11
00:00:35,070 --> 00:00:38,940
Are you saying Oh Jung Ran
tried to kill my Min Jun?

12
00:00:41,250 --> 00:00:42,250
Yes, sir.

13
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:45,380
It's the truth.

14
00:00:47,820 --> 00:00:48,850
What the...

15
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,690
Butler Ok.

16
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:55,890
- Butler Ok!
- Yes, sir.

17
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,730
What is it, sir?

18
00:00:59,130 --> 00:01:02,000
Get Oh Jung Ran in here right now!

19
00:01:02,870 --> 00:01:03,870
Yes, sir.

20
00:01:06,970 --> 00:01:08,970
Sir, why do you want her here?

21
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,280
Myung Hui, you were right all along.

22
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,850
The person who tried
to harm Min Jun...

23
00:01:16,110 --> 00:01:17,320
was Oh Jung Ran.

24
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,390
Why does he want to see me
at this hour?

25
00:01:27,290 --> 00:01:30,300
I'm not sure,
but it doesn't sound good.

26
00:01:32,430 --> 00:01:33,430
Butler Ok,

27
00:01:33,770 --> 00:01:36,000
you didn't tell him
about what I did, did you?

28
00:01:36,370 --> 00:01:38,000
It wasn't me.

29
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:39,900
It wasn't you?

30
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:44,010
Are you saying someone did talk?

31
00:01:49,450 --> 00:01:51,680
What is it? What's going on now?

32
00:01:53,650 --> 00:01:57,190
Oh Jung Ran, how dare you
go after my son...

33
00:01:58,060 --> 00:01:59,920
and try to kill him?

34
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,500
Butler Ok said she didn't talk.

35
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:06,870
Not this again.

36
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:11,070
How many times must I say it?
I have a solid alibi.

37
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,340
Who's been feeding you
this nonsense now?

38
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,540
I did.

39
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:21,710
You... Why would you?

40
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:25,180
The alibi you're talking about?
I created it for you.

41
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:28,520
I hired a double,
just like you told me.

42
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:29,820
Song Geun Tae!

43
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,160
Oh Jung Ran!

44
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:40,470
You tried to kill my Min Jun
as a newborn.

45
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,800
Wasn't that enough?

46
00:02:42,370 --> 00:02:44,770
How could you try to kill him
a second time?

47
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,680
Honey, it wasn't me.
Myung Hui set this whole thing up.

48
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:53,750
She manipulated Geun Tae
into framing me.

49
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:57,450
What? Frame you?

50
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:01,890
You, tell them the truth.
You told me yourself.

51
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,450
Kim Myung Hui blackmailed you!

52
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:04,560
It was you...

53
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:08,490
who was being blackmailed
by Butler Ok.

54
00:03:09,730 --> 00:03:12,630
Mrs. Ok,
it's time you told the truth.

55
00:03:13,330 --> 00:03:14,430
What?

56
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:17,670
Wait, what in the world is going on?

57
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,770
So you knew about this all along?

58
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:24,140
Then why did you keep it a secret?

59
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:30,780
The truth is, I overheard
their entire conversation that day.

60
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:34,050
Ms. Oh lured Mr. Min Jun
to the warehouse...

61
00:03:34,350 --> 00:03:36,550
by telling him Chloe was in danger.

62
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:40,190
I kept this to myself because
it was only circumstantial evidence.

63
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,760
I was afraid of causing trouble
for the family,

64
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:45,900
so I chose to be cautious.
I'm very sorry.

65
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:53,100
So that's why you asked me
to fire Butler Ok.

66
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:56,210
Honey, it's not what you think.

67
00:03:56,210 --> 00:03:57,440
Shut your mouth!

68
00:03:58,580 --> 00:04:00,010
If you say one more word,

69
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,810
I'll bury you where you stand.

70
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,320
Honey, please hear me out.

71
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,020
It wasn't me.

72
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:12,120
I'm telling you,
it's a trap set by Kim Myung Hui!

73
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:14,060
You're shameless
right to the very end.

74
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:15,460
Let go of me!

75
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:18,260
How dare you lay a hand on my son?

76
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:23,270
Oh Jung Ran, we are through.
You just wait.

77
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,370
Get this thing out of my sight now!

78
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:30,910
- Honey, please. No, I...
- Let go!

79
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:35,110
No, let go of me. Get off me!

80
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:36,380
Honey, please.

81
00:04:36,650 --> 00:04:37,880
- Honey!
- Get out.

82
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:41,690
Let go of me. Honey! Hey!

83
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:46,020
Jung Ran.

84
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:48,260
Kim Myung Hui, you.

85
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,030
What on earth did you say to him?

86
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,530
What secret are you holding
over his head?

87
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,770
Park Tae Ho and Song Geun Tae.

88
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:02,470
You said they could never leave you.

89
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:06,810
They could never betray you, right?

90
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:12,920
And yet, here you are,
betrayed by the people you trusted.

91
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,660
I wonder
if that makes it sting more,

92
00:05:18,290 --> 00:05:19,890
if it makes you feel
just how unfair it really is.

93
00:05:21,530 --> 00:05:22,960
I certainly hope it does.

94
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,160
You...

95
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,360
You!

96
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,170
You should've left my son alone.

97
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:30,570
After all I've done
to raise and protect him,

98
00:05:31,170 --> 00:05:32,500
you dare try to kill him again?

99
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:34,970
What are you talking about?

100
00:05:40,450 --> 00:05:41,450
Hyun Jun!

101
00:05:43,610 --> 00:05:44,620
Hyun Jun.

102
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,490
Hyun Jun.

103
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:50,560
What on earth...

104
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,560
Mom.

105
00:05:57,260 --> 00:06:00,360
Did you try to kill Min Jun?

106
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:04,440
Don't tell me...

107
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,270
Were you behind the hit-and-run?

108
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,980
Min Jun and even Chloe...

109
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:18,150
Did they almost die because of you?

110
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:23,250
Hyun Jun, no, that's not it.
Please hear me out.

111
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:26,460
What sort of monster does that?

112
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:32,160
Even after I learned you'd killed
someone before, you did it again?

113
00:06:33,330 --> 00:06:34,330
Again?

114
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:38,440
If you cared about me at all,
you wouldn't have done it.

115
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:45,710
How could you do this, knowing
how crushed I was to be your son?

116
00:06:47,380 --> 00:06:49,080
Everything I did was for you!

117
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,820
Everything I ever did was for you.

118
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:59,520
I only wanted to fill your path
with flowers, not thorns.

119
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:02,630
My only crime was trying my best.

120
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,800
Jung Ran, please.

121
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:05,630
That's enough.

122
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,540
Right.

123
00:07:12,970 --> 00:07:14,270
So I was the problem all along.

124
00:07:17,110 --> 00:07:19,280
Because of me,
an innocent person died.

125
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:24,820
I'm the reason
Min Jun and Chloe got hurt.

126
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,290
I...

127
00:07:30,290 --> 00:07:31,620
I'm the one who should've died.

128
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:39,030
Hyun Jun! Hyun Jun, please!

129
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:40,460
Hyun Jun.

130
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:44,400
- Hyun Jun...
- Hyun Jun!

131
00:07:44,470 --> 00:07:46,100
- Hyun Jun!
- Hyun Jun!

132
00:07:47,470 --> 00:07:49,910
Hyun Jun!

133
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,210
Jung Ran, oh no.

134
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:04,160
How could you do this to me? How?

135
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:07,060
The whole world
could've betrayed me,

136
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,330
but not you.

137
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,800
How could you give in
to Kim Myung Hui's blackmail...

138
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:15,330
and turn against me?

139
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:25,010
It was for Hyun Jun.

140
00:08:27,980 --> 00:08:29,010
If you'd...

141
00:08:29,850 --> 00:08:32,180
gone after Park Min Jun again
and killed him,

142
00:08:33,550 --> 00:08:34,720
then our Hyun Jun...

143
00:08:35,820 --> 00:08:39,060
would truly become a murderer's son.

144
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:45,030
I couldn't let that happen
to our Hyun Jun.

145
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,370
Because he's my son.

146
00:08:58,510 --> 00:08:59,640
Who are you calling your son?

147
00:09:00,310 --> 00:09:02,510
Hyun Jun is my son
and Park Tae Ho's son!

148
00:09:04,050 --> 00:09:05,180
He's as precious
as my own life to me.

149
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:10,020
He's my son.
He's more precious than life itself.

150
00:09:11,990 --> 00:09:12,990
My son...

151
00:09:14,130 --> 00:09:15,130
My son!

152
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:32,280
I'm relieved...

153
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,680
that even a monster like you...

154
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:37,720
still treasures her son.

155
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:42,390
Now that you've torn
Hyun Jun's heart apart,

156
00:09:42,890 --> 00:09:44,060
are you satisfied?

157
00:09:45,290 --> 00:09:46,290
Well,

158
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,490
I don't think
I'm satisfied just yet.

159
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,560
What?

160
00:09:53,730 --> 00:09:54,730
Mr. Song.

161
00:09:56,070 --> 00:09:58,540
it seems you haven't told her yet...

162
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,980
that I know exactly...

163
00:10:07,950 --> 00:10:09,650
who Hyun Jun's father is.

164
00:10:15,650 --> 00:10:16,650
You...

165
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,390
Don't tell me you...

166
00:10:22,990 --> 00:10:24,260
Don't you worry.

167
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:28,930
I haven't told the chairman yet.

168
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,070
I plan to milk this secret...

169
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,840
very slowly,

170
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:37,680
for as long as I can.

171
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,510
Slowly,

172
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:42,410
for as long as you can?

173
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:45,850
What on earth
are you planning to do?

174
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:49,850
First, I'm going to get you divorced
and out of the picture.

175
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:55,530
Then I'll make sure
you can't ever hurt Min Jun again.

176
00:10:56,060 --> 00:11:00,430
After that, you'll watch
as my son takes over Adele.

177
00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:03,270
As if I'd let you...

178
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:04,940
You'll do exactly that...

179
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:07,770
if you want to keep your son
in this house...

180
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,670
and at Adele Group.

181
00:11:12,410 --> 00:11:13,410
What?

182
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:17,950
I think I'll use your son's life
as leverage,

183
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:22,050
so you'll never dare lay a hand
on my son again.

184
00:11:22,650 --> 00:11:24,260
So if I go after your son,

185
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:27,290
you'll reveal Hyun Jun's secret?

186
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:29,290
Precisely.

187
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:31,460
So you'll live...

188
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:36,130
in constant fear
that your secret will be exposed.

189
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:39,640
You'll despair knowing
that I control...

190
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,570
his future.

191
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:45,240
Day after day,

192
00:11:46,110 --> 00:11:48,180
you'll live in agony.

193
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,990
Oh no.

194
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:10,670
My poor Hyun Jun.

195
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,190
Park Hyun Jun?

196
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:32,520
Wait.

197
00:12:34,430 --> 00:12:36,660
Please, just stay like this
for a minute.

198
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:41,400
What's wrong? What happened?

199
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:48,970
I just...

200
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,040
My very existence disgusts me.

201
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:56,350
What is it? Why are you saying that?

202
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:02,550
I'm a murderer's son,
through and through.

203
00:13:06,890 --> 00:13:09,260
As if my father wasn't enough,
now my mother too.

204
00:13:13,530 --> 00:13:15,170
In the past, my mom...

205
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:20,240
killed someone.

206
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:25,780
But even after I found out
all about it,

207
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:29,750
she still tried to kill
Park Min Jun and you.

208
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:37,290
My mom... my own mother...
I'm so sorry.

209
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:41,630
I'm so sorry.

210
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:02,980
It's not your fault.

211
00:14:21,570 --> 00:14:22,570
Seriously?

212
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:29,040
What's put you in such a good mood,
grinning like that?

213
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:32,910
She's right. You look happier
than I've seen you in a while.

214
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:37,480
I just keep thinking about
what happened yesterday.

215
00:14:38,650 --> 00:14:39,720
Yesterday?

216
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,950
Wait, hold on.

217
00:14:42,220 --> 00:14:45,060
You did what I said
and got your position back?

218
00:14:45,660 --> 00:14:47,120
Yesterday...

219
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:50,090
I put my heart first, not my job.

220
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:52,000
- What?
- What?

221
00:14:52,630 --> 00:14:54,270
Min Jun, he...

222
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:59,270
He held me in his arms
for the first time.

223
00:15:08,650 --> 00:15:10,410
I was so happy yesterday.

224
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:14,750
For crying out loud.
All this fuss over one measly hug?

225
00:15:14,890 --> 00:15:19,560
This is no time for that, you hear?
You need to get your job back.

226
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:20,920
Now, now.

227
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:25,160
She said things are going well.
You don't have to be so harsh.

228
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:30,000
Don't worry.
I think Min Jun's falling for me.

229
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:34,200
Now I'm going back to the company
to reclaim my position.

230
00:15:35,070 --> 00:15:38,940
I can have it all.
Min Jun and my position.

231
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:52,860
Where's Hyun Jun?
Did he leave already?

232
00:15:56,060 --> 00:15:59,030
Oh Jung Ran. How dare she...

233
00:16:01,130 --> 00:16:03,530
Father, did something happen?

234
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:07,100
Let's eat breakfast first.

235
00:16:08,070 --> 00:16:09,770
Something's really off here.

236
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:11,640
Well...

237
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,910
Nothing's wrong.

238
00:16:14,410 --> 00:16:18,820
Don't worry about anything else.
Just focus on getting better.

239
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:24,720
I'm feeling a lot better,
so I'd like to go back to work.

240
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:25,790
Is that okay?

241
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,960
You want to go back to work so soon?

242
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:31,300
What if you get another headache
at work?

243
00:16:31,530 --> 00:16:34,770
Being at the company
actually boosted my confidence.

244
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:38,770
If it helps me regain my memory,
I think it's worth a shot.

245
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:42,670
Yes, of course. Sure.

246
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:47,610
That's my boy. You can handle it.
Go ahead and start today.

247
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:48,680
Good.

248
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,880
Are you sure you're well enough
to go back to work?

249
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:58,320
Don't worry. If I start to feel off,
I'll head straight to the hospital.

250
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:02,860
By the way, Mother,
what did you do...

251
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:04,630
with Hyun Jun's secret?

252
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:09,870
I'm not going to tell the chairman.

253
00:17:10,600 --> 00:17:13,170
That's all I can promise you.

254
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,870
That's more than enough.

255
00:17:17,140 --> 00:17:18,210
Thank you.

256
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:34,260
Oh Jung Ran!

257
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:37,260
The more I think about it,
the more I can't forgive her.

258
00:17:37,630 --> 00:17:40,460
She had the audacity
to try to kill my son,

259
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:45,070
but she also used the very trap
I laid for Chloe.

260
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:49,910
There was no useful CCTV footage
after Min Jun's accident,

261
00:17:49,970 --> 00:17:52,180
so I completely shot myself
in the foot!

262
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:54,810
I've been regretting it ever since.

263
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:04,620
What now?

264
00:18:05,390 --> 00:18:06,820
Is this about Oh Jung Ran?

265
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:10,360
What are you going to do
about Ms. Oh?

266
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:15,130
Myung Hui,
what do you want me to do?

267
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:18,200
Please divorce her.

268
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:21,100
Divorce her?

269
00:18:21,410 --> 00:18:24,610
As long as she remains
the lady of Adele Group,

270
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:27,110
she'll continue to be a threat
to our Min Jun.

271
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:30,380
If you decide to go through with it,

272
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:32,920
I'll make sure the divorce papers
get signed myself.

273
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:37,790
I'll handle Oh Jung Ran myself.
You stay out of it.

274
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:40,620
We can't have the police
or the press...

275
00:18:41,090 --> 00:18:42,460
getting involved in this.

276
00:18:42,530 --> 00:18:45,760
You're going to cover this up,
even though this is about Min Jun?

277
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:49,330
If the culprit is family,
we keep it in the family.

278
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:52,840
Don't blow this out of proportion
for no reason.

279
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:04,550
By the way,

280
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:06,620
about Driver Song...

281
00:19:08,890 --> 00:19:12,460
Were you the one
who made him confess?

282
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,290
I don't know what you mean.

283
00:19:15,990 --> 00:19:19,200
He's not someone
who'd ever betray Jung Ran.

284
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:22,370
But he changed his mind
and confessed.

285
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:26,270
There must be a good reason for it.

286
00:19:27,140 --> 00:19:28,370
Just like Jung Ran said,

287
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:32,440
I'm wondering if you threatened him.

288
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:35,210
Threaten him?

289
00:19:35,910 --> 00:19:37,280
She's just making excuses.

290
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:40,820
Fine.

291
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:43,690
In any case, Myung Hui,
stay out of it.

292
00:19:51,930 --> 00:19:54,030
He wants to treat
the threat to Min Jun's life...

293
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:55,730
as a family matter?

294
00:19:57,430 --> 00:19:58,440
A family matter?

295
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,750
Find Driver Song
and bring him to me.

296
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:11,580
I need to know what deal he made...

297
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:13,450
with Kim Myung Hui.

298
00:20:13,850 --> 00:20:14,850
Yes, sir.

299
00:20:15,490 --> 00:20:16,790
Should I bring Ms. Oh as well?

300
00:20:18,560 --> 00:20:20,520
I'll deal with Oh Jung Ran later.

301
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:28,670
Set the stage perfectly for her.

302
00:20:30,300 --> 00:20:34,810
How dare she try to kill my son
in a game that I myself set up?

303
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:38,340
I can't let her
get away with that, can I?

304
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:40,580
Yes, I understand.

305
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:42,750
- Make no mistakes.
- Yes, sir.

306
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:55,830
Chairman Park...

307
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,400
Is he planning to kill Jung Ran?

308
00:21:10,910 --> 00:21:12,280
Didn't you leave already?

309
00:21:13,280 --> 00:21:16,710
You weren't there for breakfast,
so I assumed you left early.

310
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:19,380
You...

311
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:23,990
You don't know about yesterday,
do you?

312
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:25,520
Yesterday?

313
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:31,360
I knew something felt off.
Did something happen?

314
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,130
Your hit-and-run.

315
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,240
My mom was behind it.

316
00:21:44,910 --> 00:21:45,910
What?

317
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:49,380
Knowing your mother,
she'll want to do this by the book.

318
00:21:50,910 --> 00:21:53,580
I figured you'd find out anyway,
so I wanted to tell you myself.

319
00:21:57,020 --> 00:21:58,160
Wait, how...

320
00:22:00,890 --> 00:22:01,890
Why on earth?

321
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:04,730
Why would your mother do that to me?

322
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:07,160
She said she did it for my sake.

323
00:22:09,630 --> 00:22:11,440
Maybe I shouldn't have been born.

324
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:15,340
I feel like I was born...

325
00:22:17,010 --> 00:22:19,340
just to get in the way of your life.

326
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:27,920
The Park Hyun Jun I know
wouldn't say this.

327
00:22:28,250 --> 00:22:29,490
You're the one who always said...

328
00:22:30,320 --> 00:22:32,060
you and your mother
aren't a package deal.

329
00:22:33,320 --> 00:22:35,030
What happened
during the time I can't remember...

330
00:22:35,030 --> 00:22:36,290
that made you so serious?

331
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:40,060
You nearly died
and even lost your memories.

332
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:45,300
Honestly, I can't say
that I forgive your mother.

333
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:48,970
But I don't care whose son you are.

334
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:51,070
To me, you're always Park Hyun Jun.

335
00:22:51,070 --> 00:22:52,880
I don't know about our parents,

336
00:22:53,210 --> 00:22:56,050
but I want things to stay that way
between us.

337
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:58,850
When your memory returns,

338
00:22:59,350 --> 00:23:01,050
will you still be able to say that?

339
00:23:02,090 --> 00:23:03,650
When you see me with Baek Jin Ju,

340
00:23:04,420 --> 00:23:06,320
will you still be as understanding
as you are now?

341
00:23:10,730 --> 00:23:11,730
I'm sorry.

342
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:18,140
I'm sorry for everything.

343
00:23:20,170 --> 00:23:21,370
That's why I'm warning you...

344
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,110
not to trust Choi Yu Na too much.

345
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:26,740
What?

346
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:29,550
Don't trust her blindly
and see her for who she really is.

347
00:23:31,210 --> 00:23:33,880
Didn't we get along?

348
00:23:35,350 --> 00:23:36,350
Well...

349
00:23:37,950 --> 00:23:39,060
You'll have to find out
for yourself.

350
00:23:42,630 --> 00:23:43,630
But...

351
00:23:49,970 --> 00:23:52,700
To celebrate Director Park Min Jun's
return, it's my treat.

352
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,970
Please, order whatever you'd like.

353
00:23:57,570 --> 00:23:59,680
Why are you treating us
to celebrate his return...

354
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:00,940
when you've already resigned?

355
00:24:05,420 --> 00:24:08,390
Because we're in love.
I'm just supporting my man.

356
00:24:10,850 --> 00:24:13,420
Does that mean
you're coming back too?

357
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:16,330
I imagine that's how
things will play out.

358
00:24:17,360 --> 00:24:19,130
You two like street food, right?

359
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:21,630
I'm actually craving
something sweet.

360
00:24:21,630 --> 00:24:24,300
From snacks
to full meals and dessert,

361
00:24:24,370 --> 00:24:26,840
we've prepared everything for you
to enjoy at once.

362
00:24:27,270 --> 00:24:28,570
So feel free to take your time
and choose.

363
00:24:35,750 --> 00:24:37,710
So, is everyone happy?

364
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:41,950
Yes, it's great that
there's something here for everyone.

365
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:44,550
Yes, the food is delicious.

366
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:47,120
- I agree.
- Thank you.

367
00:24:47,760 --> 00:24:49,860
Anyway, are you feeling
all better now?

368
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:53,160
Yes, apart from the memory loss,
I'm fine.

369
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:54,560
That's a relief.

370
00:24:56,370 --> 00:24:57,500
Enjoy your meal.

371
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:00,170
Welcome,
please have a seat over here.

372
00:25:04,740 --> 00:25:06,940
What's this? We didn't order it.

373
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,780
This one's on the house.

374
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,880
It's only
for the handsome customers.

375
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,180
Part-timers can't do that.

376
00:25:14,180 --> 00:25:15,950
The boss can just deduct it
from my pay.

377
00:25:17,320 --> 00:25:18,620
As if you make enough.

378
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,930
Just take it back.

379
00:25:25,630 --> 00:25:27,030
Who are you to decide that?

380
00:25:29,700 --> 00:25:31,770
I'm his girlfriend, got it?

381
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:34,240
You're an employee,
so just do your job.

382
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:41,880
Seriously?

383
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,350
Whatever.

384
00:25:55,460 --> 00:25:56,530
Of course.

385
00:25:57,560 --> 00:26:00,000
The person who tried to kill you
and Park Min Jun...

386
00:26:01,430 --> 00:26:02,430
Unbelievable.

387
00:26:03,870 --> 00:26:04,870
Darn.

388
00:26:06,900 --> 00:26:10,110
Poor Park Hyun Jun.
He must be a total wreck.

389
00:26:11,410 --> 00:26:12,580
For Hyun Jun,

390
00:26:13,580 --> 00:26:16,210
it's been one burden after another.

391
00:26:18,580 --> 00:26:20,920
Are you genuinely worried about him?

392
00:26:22,890 --> 00:26:25,090
It's just one terrible thing
after another.

393
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:30,490
More importantly, I need to find out
how to use this to our advantage.

394
00:26:31,860 --> 00:26:34,800
I'm going to the Adele Group
to see what's going on.

395
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,770
Are you going to see Chairman Park?

396
00:26:36,770 --> 00:26:38,900
President Kim Myung Hui, actually.

397
00:26:39,570 --> 00:26:40,570
Why her?

398
00:26:40,870 --> 00:26:42,970
Now that Oh Jung Ran's crime
has been exposed,

399
00:26:43,340 --> 00:26:46,180
she's essentially won her fight
against Oh Jung Ran.

400
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:50,050
I need to find out her next move,
so we can be ready.

401
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:53,380
Good point.

402
00:26:56,420 --> 00:26:57,720
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

403
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:02,060
Here are the divorce papers
for Chairman Park and Oh Jung Ran.

404
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,900
I've prepared them so all they need
are the signatures to make it final.

405
00:27:06,530 --> 00:27:08,100
Chairman Park told you
to stay out of it...

406
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,670
because he doesn't know
the whole story,

407
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:13,470
but we have some serious leverage
over Oh Jung Ran now.

408
00:27:14,770 --> 00:27:16,940
If you make your move,
she'll have no choice but to sign.

409
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:22,310
If I step in and force Oh Jung Ran
to divorce him...

410
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:25,820
Then Min Jun is guaranteed to become
the Adele Group's successor.

411
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:30,950
We can finally right the wrongs
done to Myung Hui.

412
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:34,560
You've been through so much,
Dan Hui.

413
00:27:38,630 --> 00:27:41,160
(Application for Divorce
by Mutual Consent)

414
00:27:46,170 --> 00:27:48,200
Until Min Jun becomes the successor,

415
00:27:48,810 --> 00:27:50,170
I can't afford to let my guard down.

416
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:52,710
I have to meet with Oh Jung Ran.

417
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:55,810
Find out where she is
and set up a meeting for me.

418
00:27:56,410 --> 00:27:57,410
Got it.

419
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:09,560
I'll head out first, then.

420
00:28:13,560 --> 00:28:14,700
What brings you here?

421
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:16,800
Hyun Jun told me.

422
00:28:17,430 --> 00:28:19,770
His mother was thrown out
of the house.

423
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:23,840
Did he also tell you
she's the one who hurt you?

424
00:28:24,810 --> 00:28:25,810
Yes.

425
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:32,050
Despite that,
you're still going to marry him?

426
00:28:32,380 --> 00:28:34,020
It's not his fault.

427
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:37,120
Does that mean
you and Park Min Jun...

428
00:28:37,690 --> 00:28:40,020
have no intention of forgiving her?

429
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:42,760
The chairman
won't forgive her either.

430
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:45,400
Now that she's been thrown out,

431
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:48,700
will you become
the new lady of the Adele Group?

432
00:28:50,930 --> 00:28:54,440
You're very interested in our family
before you've even married into it.

433
00:28:56,240 --> 00:29:00,140
It's the family I'm marrying into,
so of course I should be interested.

434
00:29:02,310 --> 00:29:05,580
Ms. Kim, it seems we have a problem.

435
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,790
What? They're gone?

436
00:29:12,520 --> 00:29:16,430
We can't locate Driver Song
or your wife.

437
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:19,330
Oh Jung Ran isn't one to give up
just because I kicked her out.

438
00:29:23,530 --> 00:29:27,970
I'd expect her to come running,
to beg forgiveness or threaten me.

439
00:29:29,610 --> 00:29:32,380
First Driver Song,
who betrayed her...

440
00:29:32,710 --> 00:29:34,740
and now Oh Jung Ran herself
has gone into hiding.

441
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,510
What on earth are they thinking?

442
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:43,190
The gallery just called.

443
00:29:43,750 --> 00:29:44,750
Your wife...

444
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:47,720
Oh Jung Ran has taken the paintings.

445
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:50,560
What? The paintings?

446
00:29:50,790 --> 00:29:52,260
CCTV footage shows her...

447
00:29:52,260 --> 00:29:55,170
entering the secure vault that
only you and she could access...

448
00:29:55,570 --> 00:29:58,000
and taking the paintings.

449
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:03,910
She took the items
we can't report as stolen.

450
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:06,310
That means she's desperate
for money.

451
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:08,280
Oh Jung Ran...

452
00:30:09,250 --> 00:30:10,850
She said she didn't want a divorce.

453
00:30:11,980 --> 00:30:13,920
Is she trying to run away instead?

454
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:17,020
Put your men on it and find her!

455
00:30:17,290 --> 00:30:18,290
Yes, sir.

456
00:30:23,190 --> 00:30:24,190
Kim Myung Hui.

457
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:28,400
Is there something...

458
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,570
you're not telling me?

459
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:33,340
Oh Jung Ran and Driver Song.

460
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:37,470
This isn't like them,
and it's bothering me.

461
00:30:38,370 --> 00:30:39,940
If you're hiding something,
tell me now.

462
00:30:40,740 --> 00:30:44,210
She must've run away
to avoid the divorce.

463
00:30:45,620 --> 00:30:47,950
Then, I'll head to the gallery...

464
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:50,390
and confirm
which paintings are missing.

465
00:30:51,750 --> 00:30:55,860
To get into the vault that only
you and Oh Jung Ran can access,

466
00:30:56,260 --> 00:30:57,730
I'll need the passcode.

467
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,400
Forget it.

468
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:04,200
I'll go to the vault myself.
You just stay here.

469
00:31:11,410 --> 00:31:15,110
So he won't even give me
the passcode?

470
00:31:25,290 --> 00:31:28,930
The phone is currently turned off.
Leave a message after the tone.

471
00:31:28,990 --> 00:31:30,430
Call charges will apply.

472
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:33,060
Oh Jung Ran.

473
00:31:33,730 --> 00:31:37,130
Don't you forget that
I hold your son's life in my hands.

474
00:31:37,830 --> 00:31:40,970
Come sign the divorce papers
and put an end to this.

475
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,710
Remember what's at stake
for your son...

476
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,710
every time you make a move.

477
00:32:39,430 --> 00:32:42,470
(Pearl in Red)

478
00:32:42,730 --> 00:32:45,540
I at least gave you a chance,
you know.

479
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:48,100
You're the one
who made me like this!

480
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:51,710
I wish you would never
get your memory back.

481
00:32:52,180 --> 00:32:57,110
I wish you'd forget Jin Ju and Chloe
and just smile at me, and only me.

482
00:32:58,210 --> 00:33:01,450
Oh Jung Ran's cornered.
Who knows what she'll do?

483
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:04,850
I'm worried about what she might do
to you to protect her secrets.

484
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:08,560
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
